{"title":"紫檀盛开","authors":["苏碧华"],"dates":[{"year":1985,"month":1,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"紫檀盛开"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苏碧华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1981—1983年，笔者在缅甸进修。回国前，与同窗缅甸女友一起游览仰光大金塔，正值紫檀花盛开的时节。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你和我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捧着紫檀花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相约来到大金塔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天边晚霞似锦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"塔上灯火辉煌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"香客如织，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"香火缭绕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金色的紫檀花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘散着细细的清香。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你问我："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“是否喜爱紫檀花？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我回答："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我将永远怀念它。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你献上手中的花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为我祈祷："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“事事如愿以偿。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我供上金色的花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深深祝愿："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“友谊如紫檀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远灿烂、芬芳。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你报以微笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为我祝福："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“一路平安！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在返校的路上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你我无言相望。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我采一串紫檀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深情地戴在你的青丝上；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你摘一串紫檀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲切地别在我的衣襟上。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}